	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Libellos, quos requiris, curavi per bibliopolas nostros ex mercatu <placeName ref="l157" cert="high">Franckfortense</placeName> adferri.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Catalogus vero librorum hic excusorum hoc semestri haberi non potuit ob chalcographorum occupationes ad nundinas sese parantium; sed ubi reversi fuerint, efficiam ut prima occasione accipias.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Affini tuo, sicut confidis mihi, non deero et intendam in omnes occasiones; sic enim meretur non solum tua in me benevolentia, sed beneficia etiam, quibus immerentem prosequeris, quorum nomine graciam tibi magnam habeo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tractatum De iustificatione accepi et <persName ref="p1283" cert="high">Gesneri</persName> nostri librum secundum de oviparis quadrupedibus; utroque oblector et erudior.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentinam</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l411" cert="low">Richemvylam</placeName> dimisi reliquos, sicut cupivisti.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Novi praeter ea, quae ipse cognovisti, nihil accepi, nisi quod <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p714">Celius</persName> noster significavit in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> duos exercitus collectos, alterum a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1956">Suffolciae</placeName> duce, alterum ab <placeName type="citizen_name">Oveto</placeName>, atque eatenus eos in colloquium reginae (quod ambit) consensisse, ut obses detur episcopus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l553">Vindonensis</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caesarem item in procinctu habuisse expeditionem, qua traiiceret in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Angliam</placeName> reginae subventurus, sed submonitum a quibusdam habiturum a tergo infestissimum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galli</placeName> exercitum, si moveat pedem, itque mutato consilio substitisse.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cęterum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglus</placeName> quidam his diebus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8126" cert="high">Oporino</persName> nostro significavit reginam de hostibus suis devictis triumphare, qui utinam vanus sit; verum, qui has perfert et ipse de <placeName type="citizen_name">Oveto</placeName> capto narrabit, quod <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentorati</placeName> accepit.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale cum uxore, liberis et symmistis fratribus, quos cupio meis verbis reverenter salutes.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> 8a marcii anno 1554.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3099" cert="high">Sulcerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Viro praestantissimo d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, ecclesiae Tigurinae antistiti, domino et symmistae colendissimo suo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
